{
  "texts": [
    "Thus, we used the R-GCN for further knowledge discovery of NPIs on AD prevention.",
    "For open LBD tasks, Fig. 2 displays the Precision-Recall and Receiver Operating Characteristic (ROC) curves for the six models under both time slicing and clinical trials testing conditions.",
    "In the time slicing evaluation, the RGCN model stood out by achieving the highest Area Under the ROC Curve (AUROC) of 0.74 and the highest Area Under the Precision-Recall Curve (AUPR) of 0.74.",
    "Similarly, in the clinical trials evaluation, it maintained superior performance with the highest AUROC of 0.79 and an AUPR of 0.80.",
    "Subsequently, we utilized t-SNE (t-distributed stochastic neighbor embedding) 52 to obtain the two-dimensional projection of the learned node representations."
  ]
}